1. Push local changes to remote repository
File on remote changed
Files on GitHub - not changed

git add
git commit
git push


2. Pull remote changed to local using fetch and merge or pull
File on GitHub changed
File on local - not changed

git fetch (origin - repo name, if many repos attached to the remote repo on PC)
git merge origin/branch_name - подтянуть изменения с сервера (удалённого репозитория), если upstream
git merge branch_name - слить 2 ветки: branch_name в ту, в которой находишься/выполняешь эту команду
git merge - подтянуть изменения из локальной upstream ветки, если она настроена (main - origin/main)

Если upstream ветка не задана
git fetch origin main
git mege origin/main

Или просто
git pull origin main

Если upstream ветка задана
git fetch
git merge

Или просто
git pull


3. Pull before push
File on GitHub changed
Same file on remote - changed too

git add
git commit
git push > error
git pull
> resolve conflicts via editor
> PyCharm can make git add of changed files automatically, if not - git add
git commit
git push


4. Fetch and add, commit, pull before push
File on GitHub changed
Same file on remote - changed too

git fetch (not git add, commit, push)
git pull > error: Your local changes to the following files would be overwritten by merge
Please commit your changes or stash them before you merge
git add
git commit
git pull
> If no conflicts (changes in different files, or lines of code of the same file) - the vim redactor is displayed
> If conflicts are present - resolve them
git push


5. Fetch, stash, pull before push (no conflicts)
File on GitHub changed
Same file on remote - changed too

git fetch
git stash
git pull
git stash pop (changed in different files, or lines of code of the same file)
git add
git commit
git push

git stash doesnt work after add, commit ?
git stash не затрагивает уже закоммиченные изменения
git stash временно сохраняет незакоммиченные изменения в рабочем каталоге и индексе


6. Fetch, stash, pull before push (with conflicts)
File on GitHub changed
Same file on remote - changed too
git fetch
git stash
git pull
git stash pop (remote and local files changed on the same line)
> Conflicts in the changed file
> Resolve all conflicts via UI feature
> PyCharm can make git add of changed files automatically, if not - git add
git commit
git push

